{
  "texts": [
    "From it we can observe that SAM consistently achieves superiority across all datasets on all evaluation metrics.",
    "In particular, outperforms other baselines on CIDEr score by a large margin of 5.3 (37%) on group captioning and 4.63 (22%) on storytelling, which demonstrates that SAM generates more accurate and comprehensive answers.",
    "Beyond this, we find that the improvement of our method mainly manifests in two aspects:1) Enhance the ability to follow instructions that require identifying multi-image correlations.",
    "We observe that many MLLMs struggle to follow instructions for identifying correlations, such as interpreting storytelling tasks through image captions.",
    "This leads to their answers containing only some keywords rather than coherent story descriptions."
  ]
}